.SH DESCRIPTION
.B LS 
Displays animations aimed to correct users who accidentally enter 
.B LS 
instead of 
.BR ls . 
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-a
An accident seems to happen. You'll feel pity for people who cry for help.
.TP
.B \-l
shows little one.
.TP
.B \-F
It flies.
.TP
.B \-e
Allow interrupt by Ctrl+C.
.PP
